--- !u!114 &717445864
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 717445861}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 454e4fe846edaaf4991a31ee3962652f, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueTrigger
  dialogue:
    dialogueSets:
    - entries:
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b830962503541af4991268c47b0ba3c4, type: 3}
        sentence: ...                    ...                    ...
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 61f5cdb39cb9c9746ab3495fda996c4b, type: 3}
        sentence: 'Took your time Maurice, you got the dough? '
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 61f5cdb39cb9c9746ab3495fda996c4b, type: 3}
        sentence: Non descript mumbles
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 61f5cdb39cb9c9746ab3495fda996c4b, type: 3}
        sentence: Good, first time you did something right. Had us worried when the
          comms cut out, thought you somehow screwed up.
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 61f5cdb39cb9c9746ab3495fda996c4b, type: 3}
        sentence: Okay Vick, get us moving.
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 61f5cdb39cb9c9746ab3495fda996c4b, type: 3}
        sentence: Yes boss.
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: Oh by the way, Maurice.
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: (non descript mumbles)
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: "Relax relax, just wanted to say good job today. You finally did
          something to make the family proud for once. That\u2019s worth congratulating."
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: (non descript mumbles)
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: "Yes yes, you\u2019re off the hook now. You can go back to your
          restaurant, just don\u2019t get our guys sick again alright?"
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: (short mumble)
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: "Alright boss, we\u2019re here."
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: Good. Alright Maurice, you can get out now. Just leave the bags
          in the back.
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: Oh and Maurice, before you go.
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: (short non descript mumble)
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: Just wanted to say next time you think you got the recipe, try
          your cooking yourself for once. Leave the boys out of it.
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: (short mumble)
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: Alright take care now, Vick get us outta here.
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 03842fb2a527971489697559ea90cb2d, type: 3}
        sentence: Yes Boss, See ya Maurice.
    - entries:
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -269628872, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "What do you mean you\u2019re sick? There ain\u2019t no sick in
          this business, Tony!"
      - speaker: Phone
        portrait: {fileID: -269628872, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: Mumble... Mumble >:(
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -269628872, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "Hey. Look, alright. We\u2019ll figure this out, yeah? Surely the
          other guys\u2019ll be around to-"
      - speaker: Phone
        portrait: {fileID: -269628872, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: MUMBLE! >:(
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -1348697374, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "YOU\u2019RE JOKING? YOU\u2019RE ALL SICK? HOW WE S\u2019POSED
          TO ROB A BANK WITHOUT YOU MORONS? "
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -1348697374, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "HOW WE S\u2019POSED TO GET THE CHEDDAR WITH NO COWS? HOW WE S\u2019POSED
          TO MAKE SOME GOD DAMN DOUGH WITHOUT THE FLOUR? YOU PEOPLE- "
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -1348697374, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: Boss!
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -1348697374, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "WHAT? CAN\u2019T YOU SEE I\u2019M ON THE PHONE RIGHT NOW? COME
          ONNNN!"
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -1348697374, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "God damnit, get that look off your face, Vick. I know you\u2019re
          a stand-up guy. I didn\u2019t mean to go off at you. What is it?"
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -1348697374, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "They was at uh\u2026 Maurices\u2019 pizza place last night to
          celebrate before the big day\u2026 surely if they\u2019re all sick\u2026"
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -1348697374, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "Course they was at Maurices\u2019\u2026 Come on, gotta go pay
          \u2018im another visit. Not his first slip up, I reckon it's about time
          we make him pay his dues. Get the van ready, Vick."
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -1348697374, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: Yes boss!
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -1234331770, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: Hey Maurice, word on the street is our boys ate here last night.
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: -1234331770, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "Yeah, a large group of \u2018em were in. Trying a new attempt
          at the recipe. I\u2019ll need to ask what they thought."
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -1234331770, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: Well, Maurice, they got sick. So, not only did you fail at recreating
          the family recipe, again, but you also screwed up this job we had, again.
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -1234331770, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "Oh-\u2026"
      - speaker: Mobster 1
        portrait: {fileID: -1234331770, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "Save it, I\u2019m not interested in your half baked excuses. You\u2019re
          going to do the job for us. Vick can give you the run down. I expect you
          to be out in 10, if not I\u2019ll drag you out myself."
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "Sorry about him Maurice\u2026 you uh, you know what he\u2019s
          like with this stuff. \u2018specially after what uh, you know, what happened
          with you losing Nonnas\u2019 recipe way back."
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "Yeah\u2026 I know. Least you don\u2019t hold it against me, Vick."
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "It\u2019s in the past, anyways\u2026 for the more recent slip
          up. I should give you the run down of the job. Planned this big heist on
          the Russos\u2019 Dough Production Facility."
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "The Russos\u2026 the same scumbags that stole our recipe?"
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "That\u2019s right, their place is under construction which means
          security details are light. Gave the perfect opportunity for our men before,
          y\u2019know, you got them sick. "
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: Which is why we need you to do it, not much time left on this opportunity.
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: 'We will drop you off nearby, get you to sneak into the facility
          and from the outside give you guidance to reach the secret vault room they
          have. '
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "Once you find it, you\u2019ll need to grab as much of the sweet
          dough as you can and scram. Meeting us back outside so we can make off."
      - speaker: Maurice
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: Just to be clear, by dough you mean-
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: "Yes, dough, cheddar, money. We just need you to grab as much as
          you can. Now, just \u2018cause security is lighter doesn\u2019t mean there
          won\u2019t be obstacles. So, you\u2019ll need to be well prepared."
      - speaker: Vick
        portrait: {fileID: -981673167, guid: c07f9d5398500174d84381c32d1724c5, type: 3}
        sentence: ' Grab some tools that are good for different jobs, unscrewing,
          breaking, and hitting things from afar. The whole shebang. Once you got
          everything you think you need, come meet us outside in the van.'
  done: 0
  triggerStart: 1
